  <brief_title>Effectiveness Study of Resection of Primary Tumor in Stage IV Colorectal Cancer Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Palliative Resection of Asymptomatic Primary Tumor Following Effective Induction Chemotherapy in Colorectal Cancer Patients With Unresectable Distant Metastasis: a Multi-center, Prospective, Randomized Controlled Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
